descript.abstract: This dataset contains boundary information for Virginia Department of Game and Inland Fisheries' (VDGIF) Wildlife Management Areas (WMA). The coverage includes all WMAs within Virginia. These data are formatted as an ArcView shapefile compiled by the VDGIF Fish and Wildlife Information Services (FWIS) from the VDGIF Capital Outlay database. These data are presented as polygons of each site boundary.
descript.purpose: This dataset shows boundary location of Virginia Department of Game and Inland Fisheries' Wildlife Management Areas.

dataqual.logic: The boundaries of each wildlife management area are defined to the best of our current knowledge. Exact boundary definition is not known for some areas of some WMAs.

procstep.procdesc: Boundary information was gathered from multiple sources as deemed necessary. Ground survey information was used where available. Most boundaries were drawn on 1:24000 scale USGS topographic maps according to the best available information. The boundaries were then digitized from these paper maps. Newer WMAs were on-screen digitized using USGS Digital Raster Graphics or from actual survey data.
